com.vmware.o11n.sdk.rest.client.services
Class ParameterExtractor

java.lang.Object
  com.vmware.o11n.sdk.rest.client.services.ParameterExtractor

public final class ParameterExtractor
extends Object

Fluent api for extracting Parameter objects by their name from collections of Parameter. Many entities are described by a collection of parameters, most notably WorkflowExecution and ExecutionContext. Saves keystrokes and your sanity.

See Also:
WorkflowExecution, Configuration, ExecutionContext
